      • merge

        void merge(PlasmaNode dataNode,
         java.util.HashSet<PlasmaDataObject> oldValues,
         java.util.List<PlasmaEdge> currentEdges)
           throws java.io.IOException
        Determines which object the user intentionally removed and/or added based on the change summary of the client graph. Then removes and/or adds to the existing collection, just what the user has indicated.

        Note: the client edge collection can be the results from a slice query where not all the collection results are returned. We don't want to remove what we DON'T find in the commit graph in this case.
        Throws:
        java.io.IOException
        Parameters:
        oldValueList -
        currentEdges -
